column1: 1. I used control CTRL + H to check for missing values(N/A) and errors(#)  in all sheets.
2. I selected the whole sheet, clicked on data, selected data cleanup and choose Remove duplicates.
This step was applied in all the sheets.
3. I selected the whole sheet, clicked on data, selected data cleanup and choose Trim whitspace.
This step was applied in all the sheets.
5. Fixed inconsistent text cases using =PROPER() for name categories and =UPPER() for binary categories like gender.
6. Standardized the date format to MM-DD-YY format.
